-- MagicaVoxel .vox importer. Parses the first model (SIZE + XYZI) and the
-- RGBA palette, converting MagicaVoxel's Z-up coordinates to Chunkr's Y-up
-- (mv.x -> x, mv.z -> y, mv.y -> z). Modern scene-graph chunks (nTRN, nGRP,
